title: DIY New Year’s Noisemakers
description: Make a racket with these last minute DIY noise-makers from Jojotastic. Just place bells, buttons, beads, dice and other jingly items into Ziploc® containers and shake!

transcripts: Happy new year! today we'll be making last-minute noisemakers perfect for bringing in the new year. It's really quite simple to make your last minute noise maker. sSmply fill a Ziploc container with jingly bells it could even be buttons, dice, coins whatever you have on hand. Replace the lid and tie in as bow. And then shake it. It's that easy.
